# Render import manifest: optional later
#
# Purpose:
# - enhancements, hardening, and post-launch integrations
# - not required for the minimum autonomous-alpha gate
#
# Fill only the values you intend to enable.
#
# This file is permissive:
# - empty values are allowed during import
#
# Import with:
#   RENDER_API_KEY=... RENDER_SERVICE_ID=... npm run render:import-env -- render.optional.env.example

